      <p class="blog-lead">
        Operating a <strong>polarizer cleaning machine</strong> is straightforward when you follow the right process. With correct parameters and a consistent routine, you can achieve a 99%+ cleaning yield with zero scratches. This tutorial is written for optical film production environments — follow each step to master the machine and keep defect rates near zero.
      </p>

